@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 1) Criar usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Usuario de teste"
}

### 2) Criar leilao
POST {{baseUrl}}/auction
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_name": "MacBook Pro M3",
  "category": "electronics",
  "description": "Notebook em excelente estado, bateria ok e sem marcas relevantes.",
  "condition": 1
}

### 3) Buscar leilao criado (preencher <AUCTION_ID>)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auction/<AUCTION_ID>

### 4) Buscar usuario criado (preencher <USER_ID>)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/<USER_ID>

### 5) Criar lance
POST {{baseUrl}}/bid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "<USER_ID>",
  "auction_id": "<AUCTION_ID>",
  "amount": 1500.50
}

### 6) Criar segundo lance
POST {{baseUrl}}/bid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "<USER_ID>",
  "auction_id": "<AUCTION_ID>",
  "amount": 1800.75
}

### 7) Listar lances do leilao
GET {{baseUrl}}/bid/<AUCTION_ID>

### 8) Validar vencedor
GET {{baseUrl}}/auction/winner/<AUCTION_ID>

### 9) Aguardar AUCTION_DURATION e verificar fechamento (status Closed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auction/<AUCTION_ID>

### 10) Tentar lance apos expiracao (nao deve aceitar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "<USER_ID>",
  "auction_id": "<AUCTION_ID>",
  "amount": 2100.00
}